            "content": "<p><strong>Q: What should I do if the mask doesn’t stick well?</strong></p><p><strong>A:</strong> For best results, apply the mask on freshly cleansed, slightly damp skin. Smooth it gently over your face, pressing down around the contours. Because the Salmon PDRN Mask is drenched in rich essence, some slip is normal — that’s the serum working hard to deliver deep hydration and renewal. Lying back or resting helps it adhere better and allows the ingredients to absorb more effectively.<br/></p><p><strong>Q: What ingredients are in this?</strong></p><p><strong>Salmon PDRN</strong> – The star ingredient for <strong>skin regeneration and renewal</strong>. It helps improve texture, reduce fine lines, and promote a brighter, more youthful glow by supporting cell turnover and collagen synthesis.<br/><br/><strong>Niacinamide</strong> – Brightens and refines pores, improving overall tone and clarity.<br/><br/><strong>Hyaluronic Acid</strong> – Delivers deep, lasting hydration for plumper, more supple skin.<br/><br/><strong>Peptide Complex</strong> – Strengthens the skin barrier and boosts firmness to reduce visible signs of aging.</p><p>The mask’s <strong>hydrogel base</strong> ensures slow, even absorption so your skin fully drinks in every drop of the potent serum.</p><p><strong>Q: Is this vegan and cruelty-free?</strong></p><p><strong>A:  </strong>The mask is <strong>cruelty-free</strong> — no animal testing is involved at any stage. While it contains <strong>marine collagen</strong> and <strong>salmon-derived PDRN</strong>, both are <strong>ethically and sustainably sourced</strong>. These actives are key to achieving the mask’s visible firming and rejuvenating results.<br/></p><p><strong>Q:  Do I need to sit still for 3–4 hours to get the best results?</strong></p><p><strong>A: </strong>Not at all! The mask is designed to move with you — most of our customers wear it while winding down for the night, whether that’s reading, watching TV, or getting ready for bed.</p><p>In fact, <strong>78% of users wear the mask while they sleep</strong>, and many report <strong>up to 24% better hydration and visible skin smoothness</strong> when used overnight. The longer it stays on, the more time your skin has to soak in the benefits — all while you rest.</p><p><strong>Q: Doesn’t collagen come from within? How can this penetrate the skin?</strong></p><p><strong>A:  </strong>Collagen production naturally declines with age. Our <strong>hydrolyzed marine collagen</strong> and <strong>Salmon PDRN complex</strong> help <strong>stimulate and support the skin’s natural renewal process</strong>. These smaller, bioavailable molecules penetrate the upper layers to <strong>visibly improve elasticity and bounce</strong> — complementing your skin’s internal collagen production.</p><p><strong>Q: How long do the effects last after using the mask?</strong></p><p><strong>A: </strong>You’ll notice <strong>immediate glow and plumpness</strong> after one use. With <strong>consistent weekly application</strong>, results compound — skin appears <strong>firmer, brighter, and more refined</strong> over time as the Salmon PDRN works to rejuvenate the skin barrier.</p><p><strong>Q: Can the same mask be used more than once?</strong></p><p><strong>A: </strong>No — each mask is <strong>single-use</strong> to ensure maximum potency and hygiene. Once applied, the hydrogel base releases its full concentration of Salmon PDRN and collagen actives into your skin.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QnkEdx": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does it work?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We recommend using the mask <strong>1-2 times per week</strong> for best results.<strong><br/><br/>1️⃣  Prep</strong> – Cleanse your face & apply toner or serum.<br/><br/><strong>2️⃣  Apply</strong> – Remove the mask from the pouch & peel off the protective foil.<br/><br/><strong>3️⃣  Wear</strong> – Place it on your face & leave for 1-2 hours (or until transparent).<br/><br/><strong>4️⃣  Remove</strong> – Gently take off the mask & pat in the extra essence.<br/><br/><strong>5️⃣  Glow</strong> – Enjoy hydrated, plump, and radiant skin!</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_kwzWVt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ingredients",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We do not include any harmful parabens or other nasties. We also NEVER test on animals.</p><ul><li><strong>Salmon PDRN - </strong>Known for its brightening power, this multitasking vitamin refines pores, evens tone, and boosts skin clarity.<br/></li><li><strong>Niacinamide </strong> – Known for its brightening power, this multitasking vitamin refines pores, evens tone, and boosts skin clarity.<br/></li><li><strong>Hyaluronic Acid </strong> – A hydration powerhouse that deeply moisturizes and helps retain water for plump, dewy skin.<br/></li><li><strong>Peptide - </strong> Strengthen the skin's barrier, helping it <strong>retain moisture</strong> and stay protected from environmental stressors (like pollution and UV).<br/></li></ul><p>As with all skincare products, we highly recommend & urge you please patch test the mask serum on the skin of the arm or hand before using fully as some people are more sensitive than others or have allergic reactions to blends of ingredients.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Key Benefits",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Cell Renewal & Fine Line Reduction - </strong>Powered by <strong>Salmon PDRN</strong> to support skin regeneration and smooth texture — clinically shown to reduce fine lines around the eyes by <strong>9.3%</strong> for a more youthful, radiant look.<br/><br/><strong>Deep Hydration & Barrier Strength - </strong>Enriched with <strong>hyaluronic acid and peptides</strong> to lock in moisture and reinforce the skin barrier. Delivers a <strong>79.9% boost in surface hydration</strong> and <strong>39.4% better moisture retention for 24 hours</strong>.<br/><br/><strong>Refined Texture & Radiant Glow - </strong>Improves skin texture by <strong>8.2% after just one use</strong>, while brightening dull areas, refining pores, and revealing a luminous, even-toned complexion.<br/><br/><strong>Firmness & Elasticity Boost - </strong>Formulated with <strong>Marine Collagen and PDRN</strong>, it promotes visible lifting and elasticity — proven to enhance firmness by <strong>2.9%</strong>, helping skin feel bouncier and more resilient.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_8h6X4m": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Should I wash after the mask?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>No, it is not necessary to wash your face after use. The remaining serum can be gently massaged into the skin for extra hydration.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WYG8GJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it for sensitive skin?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes! Designed to be gentle on the skin. Our mask does not strip moisture or dry out, making it ideal for all skin types.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QGc8Kr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Processing Time:</strong><br/>Once your order is placed, please allow 24 hours for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br/><br/><strong>Shipping Time:</strong><br/>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 4-8 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br/><br/><strong>Tracking Information:</strong><br/>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.</p><p><strong>Returns:<br/></strong>We want you to be fully satisfied with your purchase! If you are not completely happy with your order, we accept returns and exchanges within 60 days from the date of purchase.<br/><br/>Contact us via the website or via email: info@niforashop.com</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
