    "ss_simple_faq_NxVU6q": {
      "type": "ss-simple-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_kGtL6b": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I use the Mask?",
            "answer": "<p>🧴 <strong>Evening Routine:</strong> Cleanse and tone your face, ensuring your skin is free from oil and creams.</p><p>🎭 <strong>Application:</strong> Start with the bottom piece, followed by the top. Gently press for optimal adherence. <em>Pro tip:</em> Tilt your head back for a perfect fit.</p><p>⏳ <strong>Duration:</strong></p><p><strong>Express Glow:</strong> 1-2 hours</p><p><strong>Maximum Results:</strong> Leave it on overnight (ensure it’s fully dry to prevent shifting).</p><p>💖 <strong>The Reveal:</strong> Gently remove the mask and pat the remaining essence into your skin. <em>Pro tip:</em> Use excess serum on your neck and décolleté.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_Xpzxzp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How many masks come in a pack?",
            "answer": "<p>Each pack comes with 4 masks. Each mask is single use. We recommend starting with 2 masks per week for a month in order to get your skin glowing fast and rejuvenated. After the first month, you can use one mask per week to maintain a healthy skin.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_BDtRac": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How often & how long should I use it?",
            "answer": "<p>Use the mask 1-2 times per week for the best results. Regular use will maximize the benefits of firming, hydration, and brightening.<br/><br/>Leave the mask on for at least 60 minutes, but preferably 3-4 hours. The mask gradually becomes transparent, indicating that the nutrients are being absorbed.</p><p>For the best results, use it as a sleeping mask overnight. It does not leave any residue on your pillow.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_UdqCJ3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I use the mask alongside my other skincare products?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, the Nifora bio-collagen mask can be used in your existing skincare routine. However, we recommend testing new products on a small patch of skin to ensure they are suitable for your skin.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_3TN8mq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I use it for sensitive skin?",
            "answer": "<p>Designed to be gentle on the skin. Our mask does not strip moisture or dry out, making it ideal for all skin types.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_Y9yyii": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Should I wash my face after using the mask?",
            "answer": "<p>No, it is not necessary to wash your face after use. The remaining serum can be gently massaged into the skin for extra hydration.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_XLQhWA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What ingredients are in the mask?",
            "answer": "<p>Water, glycerin, propylene glycol, betaine, sodium carrageenan, polyurethane-35, glucomannan, 1,2-hexanediol, hydroxyacetophenone, butylene glycol, hydroxyethylcellulose, pentylene glycol, dipotassium glycyrrhizate, panthenol, potassium chloride, allantoin, tocopheryl acetate (vitamin E), niacinamide (vitamin B3), hydrolyzed collagen, hydrolyzed sodium hyaluronate, sodium hyaluronate, hydroxyphenyl propamidobenzoic acid, Glycyrrhiza Uralensis (licorice) root extract, Tremella Fuciformis (snow mushroom) extract, fructose, Centella Asiatica extract, phosphatidylcholine, phenoxyethanol, ceramide NP, copper tripeptide-1, beta-sitosterol, beta-glucan, sodium stearoyl glutamate, ethylhexylglycerin, caprylhydroxamic acid, acetyl hexapeptide-8, palmitoyl tripeptide-5.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_TCrhAW": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "60-Day Money back-guarantee?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! We stand behind the quality of our products. If you’re not satisfied with your purchase, you can request a return within 60 days of receiving your order. Simply contact our support team, and we’ll guide you through the process.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_ntbDgy": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What are the delivery times?",
            "answer": "<p><strong>Processing Time: </strong>Once your order is placed, please allow 1 business day for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br/><br/><strong>Shipping Time: </strong>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 4-8 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br/><br/><strong>Tracking Information: </strong>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
